  "title": "Payroll & Process Improvement Specialist - Up to 5.5K #HHL",
  "description": "<p><strong>West (transport at Jurong East to Tuas) </strong></p><p><strong>8.30am to 6.00pm (Monday to Thursday) & 8.30am to\n5.30pm (Friday) – Flexible working hours </strong><br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Process monthly payroll accurately and on time (including attendance, OT, and claims)</p></li><li><p>Verify timesheets and handle payroll adjustments</p></li><li><p>Manage statutory submissions (CPF, tax clearance, IR8A, government claims)</p></li><li><p>Prepare payroll, manpower costing, and variance reports using Power BI</p></li><li><p>Handle payroll-related queries from employees</p></li><li><p>Support HR audits, budgeting, and reporting activities</p></li><li><p>Lead lean management and process digitalisation initiatives</p></li><li><p>Continuously improve payroll workflows and systems</p></li><li><p>Support ad-hoc HR projects and system migrations</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Experience in payroll and/or HR operations with knowledge of Singapore labour regulations</p></li><li><p><strong>Strong Power BI skills</strong></p></li><li><p>Prior experience in <strong>process optimisation / Lean / Six Sigma</strong> is highly preferred</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and stakeholder management skills</p></li></ul><p>If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599).</p>",
